column1: dc:title: ["The Biological Standard of Living in Norway during the 18th Century and Thereafter: Does Selectivity Drive the Results? "]

dc:description: ["TThe Norwegian dataset covers military recruits which have been collected by Wiegel (2015). They cover the birth decades of the first three quarters of the 18th century and are subject to the usual military sample biases. Occupational data is not available to a large extent
column2: hence it has not been included in the dataset. The regional selection covers many different parts of Norway."]
